      "content": "yeah that makes sense. i guess i'm just a bit anxious about things going wrong or just general travel chaos. you know, the weird little things that happen with trains where everything just seems to go sideways for no apparent reason. nothing major, just annoying stuff that messes up a plan. any advice for staying calm if things get a bit chaotic?",
